<p>I was looking up videos of Kubuntu Vs. Linux Mint last night (as one does), and ended up watching Hank Green&rsquo;s video about Wikipedia.</p>
<p>The guy doesn&rsquo;t need any introduction to his passionate videos, and neither does Wikipedia. But, he made me rejoin Wikipedia and add my first edit in a long time.</p>
